  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    AbstractGraph
    An abstract class that is the superclass of every chart class.
    AverageYearTempChart
    The Charts for Average Yearly Temperature - line & scatter.
    AvgTempBarCountry
    A class containing the Average Temperature by Country Bar Chart.
    AvgTempBarCountryChange
    A class containing the Average Change in Temperature for Countries Chart sorted.
    BasicLineChart
    A class containing raw data points from the global dataset in a chart.
    EconomyAvgLineChart
    A class containing a line chart with the Top 5 World Economies Average Yearly Temperature from 1900 to 2012.
    GraphCharts

    Main
    Main is the main class for the application.
    Model
    The Model class defines all I/O from the CSV files.
    SeasonsChart
    A class containing an interactive panel with buttons to choose for different charts with one month representing each season.
    ThermometerAvgChart
    A class creating the thermometer chart's view with the "AverageYearTempChart" scatter plot model.
    View
    View creates and initializes the whole GUI of the Main application.
    The GUI uses standard Swing components with nested JPanels.
